- Always move queries into their own hooks alongside the page / component that uses them
- - File naming Format should be useGqlXxxx
- Always move buisness logic into hooks when updating components and pages
- Try and keep hooks specific to one idea, we don't want to have one massive hook
- If effects, memo's, and callbacks are complicated or could be consolidated into a hook for easier readability and file structure, move them into their own hooks